Liliane Bettencourt: François-Marie Banier convicted of exploitation of weakness
The Court of Nanterre decided on Friday to judge the artist François-Marie Banier to determine whether, as the daughter of billionaire Liliane Bettencourt claims, he has exploited a weak moment of the eighty-year-old to sneak up some of her wealth.
